    <h1>User Data Deletion Instructions</h1>
    <p><em>Last Updated: September 19, 2025</em></p>

    <p>Our game, "Click the Button Game", is designed with your privacy in =
mind. We do not create user accounts or store any personal information abou=
t you on our servers.</p>
   =20
    <p>All game-related data, such as your score, is stored locally on your=
 device within your web browser's storage.</p>

    <h2>How to Delete Your Data</h2>
    <p>To delete all data associated with the game, you can clear your brow=
ser's cache and site data. This action will reset the game and remove any s=
tored information from your device.</p>
   =20
    <p>Please refer to your browser's help section for specific instruction=
s on how to clear cache and site data.</p>


